message.line: This map is a `9`lTeam Death Match `r(TDM) map.
The objective on this map is to get more points than the other team. You can score a point for your team by defeating an enemy.
Each match is comprised of 2 teams (`4Red`r vs `9Blue`r) battling for 18 minutes.
This here is `4Red Team`r's spawn, and `9Blue Team`r's spawn is located on the opposite side.
This map has 3 and 1/2 `9`llayers`r, with an interactive water layer down the bottom of the map.
All 3 areas are accesable by all players, have fun!
Located across the bottom layer of the map are `9`lJump Pads`r. Go inside these to be launched to the top of the map.
Across the map there is water. Use `9`lFrost Walker`r to walk over it with ease, maybe even PvP with the opposing team, who knows!
All players spawn with the `9`lElytra wings`r.
Fly around the terrain with the `9`lElytra wings`r, and have fun!
Flying through `9`lItem Boxes`r gives you special perks!
Perks range from health buffs to armor improvements.
